name: Nothing Can Stop Us Execpt Money
name_original: Nothing Can Stop Us Execpt Money
description:
This time you can make it! You have a bucket list of all the destinations you would like to visit. And hope for new friendships that could begin along the way.

Nothing can stop you now!

Unless you run out of money.

CONTROLS: Arrow Keys

GOAL: Visit enough destinations and pick up enough buddies to fulfill all wishes from the bucket list

GAME OVER: Money drops to 0.

WARNING! New events, like getting additional money or meeting new friend shows only above unexplored tiles. So be wary of edges of the map or already explored territory.
